snippet.title: Vacuum Warrior Idle Game - Trailer
snippet.description:
Vacuum Warrior is a Free to Play incremental idle game. Listen to the crisp crackle of dust and debris entering your vacuum as you vacuum ridiculous amounts of dust. Upgrade your vacuums, dust, idle gains, managers, and robot vacuums. Earn achievements and explore numerous locations in the Vacuum Warrior universe!

Find it on Steam, App Store, and Google Play!

#gaming #steam #idle #indie #indiegame
